      },
      {
        title: 'Socialisation with Other Representatives Of Medical Schools',
        description: 'WIth a focus on prevention, all stakeholders were brought awareness on how to properly assess health.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Seminars and Meetings',
        description:
          'Easy and occcasion-appropriate lectures were given to students and professionals.',
